```vue
<template>
  <div>{{ result1 }} {{ result2 }}</div>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: ["url1", "url2"],
  data () {
    return {
      result1: "",
      result2: ""
    };
  },
  watch: {
    async url1 (url1) {
      this.result1 = await getPromise(url1);
    },
    async url2 (url2) {
      this.result2 = await getPromise(url2);
    }
  }
};
</script>
```

### What does the proposed API look like?

```vue
<template>
  <div>{{ result1 }} {{ result2 }}</div>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: ["url1", "url2"],
  computed: {
    result1 () {
      return getPromise(this.url1);
    },
    result2 () {
      return getPromise(this.url2);
    }
  }
};
</script>
```

